<item>
            <title>[LU-1303] LOD/OSP Implementation</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1303</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Lustre 2.0 uses old Release 1.8 client-side stack components to connect to the OSTs for stripe object pre-creation and orphan management.  Remove these components, replacing them with a new subsystem that implements transactional access to non-local OSDs to ensure a rigorous separation of client/server and server/server protocols which avoids existing recovery race conditions.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
